
<h1 class="govuk-heading-l datagovuk-heading-l">Bus statistics</h1>

<section class="govuk-section datagovuk-section">
  <p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">Get data and statistics about the local bus sector in England, Scotland and Wales. The data includes:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet datagovuk-list datagovuk-body">
  <li>quarterly bus fares statistics</li>
<li>local bus passenger journeys</li>
<li>local bus vehicle distance travelled</li>
<li>passenger distance travelled</li>
<li>costs, fares and revenue</li>
<li>government support for the bus industry and concessionary travel</li>
<li>vehicles operated by local bus operators</li>
<li>staff employed by local bus operators</li>
<li>concessionary travel</li>
<li>bus reliability and punctuality</li>
<li>historical data downloads</li>
<li>discontinued bus statistics </li>

</ul>
<p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">This data is owned by the Department for Transport. The datasets cover various time periods, and you can download them in ODS or XLS format. </p>
</section>


